  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"case-hero\" style=\"--case-bg: url(/precision/sheet-metal-fabrication.png)\">\n<div class=\"container case-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\">首页</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/industries\">行业</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/industries/consumer\">消费品</a><span>/</span><b>行业案例</b></div>\n<span>消费品案例</span>\n<h1>小家电内部支架小批试制</h1>\n<p>内部支架 / 装配固定 / 试产准备</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section case-detail-section\">\n<div class=\"container case-detail-layout\">\n<article class=\"case-story\">\n<div class=\"case-summary-grid\">\n<div><span>行业</span><strong>消费品</strong></div>\n<div><span>零件功能</span><strong>内部支架 / 装配固定 / 试产准备</strong></div>\n<div><span>制造能力</span><strong>钣金、CNC、注塑前验证、表面处理</strong></div>\n</div>\n<h2>项目场景</h2>\n<p>围绕小家电内部空间、扣位和固定方式加工支架与连接件。</p>\n<h2>方案配置</h2>\n<div class=\"case-step-grid\">\n<div><b>01</b><strong>零件功能确认</strong><span>明确装配位置、受力方式、环境条件和验证目标。</span></div>\n<div><b>02</b><strong>工艺与材料匹配</strong><span>根据尺寸、公差、表面和批次要求组合制造能力。</span></div>\n<div><b>03</b><strong>检测与交付</strong><span>围绕关键尺寸、外观状态和装配反馈输出交付资料。</span></div>\n</div>\n<h2>交付结果</h2>\n<p>支架支持装配测试和试产验证，便于后续优化模具方案。</p>\n</article>\n<aside class=\"case-aside\">\n<img alt=\"小家电内部支架小批试制\" src=\"/precision/sheet-metal-fabrication.png\"/>\n<h3>消费品制造能力</h3>\n<p>继续查看外观样机、穿戴外壳和小家电内部支架等消费品试制案例。</p>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/industries/consumer\">返回消费品行业</a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/quote#quote-upload\">提交类似需求</a>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
